Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hya-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, Shea sounds like she's pretending\Nto be from the wastelands of the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt up! Rabbit time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramming time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hya-hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! Myu wants to do that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we're letting you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you get on it later,\Nso sit tight till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa's worried about you, Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such the adoring parent!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unexpected gentleness is quite exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister Yue, Big Sister Tio's\Ndoing that heavy breathing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick, and there's no cure.\NDon't pay her any mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hya-hha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I've just been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been four months,\Nbut it feels like years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the guild leader here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? You adventurers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Loa Bawavis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a letter for you\Nfrom the Fuhren guild leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. According to this letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sounds like you went on quite the rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe newbies like you took out\Nan entire army of 60,000 troops in one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and destroyed an evil organization\Nin the course of an afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never known Ilwer to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent message!\NThere's a Demon in the labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him, Hajime Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're... Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, you've got as\Nmuch presence as a ghost, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hajime Nagumo, a gold-rank adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're part of the Hero party, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you really Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, you look like\Nyou've changed a whole lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just from your appearance and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I crawled up from the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No duh I've changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit? You're a totally different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But okay. I'm glad you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so that means you're tough\Nenough to survive down there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come into the labyrinth with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hurry, or they'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've explored so much of the labyrinth,\Nso why haven't we encountered any monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the ninetieth floor\Njust has no monsters on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki, want to head back for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about\Nthis place for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Captain Meld\Nknows something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is monster blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's blending in with the color\Nof the ground, so it's hard to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must mean there's an even\Nmore powerful monster around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that monster attacked another monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but it's hidden its tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are only tracks in this area, that\Nmeans it didn't have time to cover them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, wearing the stupidly\Nshiny armor, you're a hero, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna join up with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could join up with\Nall your friends, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My answer's not changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of your friends took us up on our offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't fool me!\NNone of us would have done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then. If you won't accept,\Nthen I have no use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let the monster have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Suzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathe in protective light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning tide and heavens, Divine Intervention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't lettin' you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engulf mine enemies, O crimson mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reckless Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reckless Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Watch out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the light of protection\Ngrow tenfold, restored by my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Intervention!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why the hell are these monsters so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyama-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna cut through them!\NYou keep the others safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You got it, Yaegashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can heal them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on a totally different level than\Nall the other monsters we've encountered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Yaegashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to ask of you\Nand your particular abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a message to Captain Meld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're an Assassin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to sneak out\Nwithout them noticing you and get to Meld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it to him, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell is with this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you taking things out\Non my daughter, you little prick? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime's totally her Papa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even think twice\Nwhen he called her his daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will he be able\Nto let his lovely daughter go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be, Hero?\NAt this rate, you're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in, and I'll prove that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O light, fill my will, sharp as a blade's edge,\Nand slice through my enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blinding Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By mine eye, all that is known\Nto my enemy shall be shut closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that will remain is their demise,\Na cold graven image.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let my enemies be crushed\Nand returned to the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crashing Gaol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taniguchi, stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies of God mayst\Nnot tread upon His holy ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Suzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taniguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heed me, O wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blustering Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They killed one of our own,\Nand we're just gonna run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurried to Captain Meld\Nto tell him about the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain is protecting a\Nteleportation circle to the 70th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Kosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others, they're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Kosuke.\NYou did what only you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for delivering the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaegashi said they'd\Ncome back on their own, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm gonna go back to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it noticed me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer are you\Ngonna keep embarrassing yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't space out!\NTell the people up above about the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what about you, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the circle on the other side!\NWe'll protect it with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's this coward's final wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Survive, Kosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the strength of the\NHeilich Kingdom Knight's resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted me to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it for me, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should just do as she says already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I also think we should do as she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you too, Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want all of us to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trust that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, if we keep trying to run away,\Nhow many of us are gonna survive this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept the reality\Nof our situation already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want us all to survive,\Nwe have to do as she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about surviving...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning, this was our war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use Limit Break now,\Nyour body won't be able to take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime Nagumo, if what Ilwer says is true,\Nthen I've got a request for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to rescue the heroes, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your friends!\NYou'll go save them, of course you will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go assuming they're my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:18:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the lot of you are no more than\Nstrangers who happen to share my homeworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed. Have you finally\Ngotten it into your thick skull now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really have no self-awareness, do you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are at war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Nagumo, save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect you, Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me a chance when you\Nrescued me, so I'm not gonna waste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you have to kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My papa's strong,\Nso he can save them for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't want to save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want, Hajime.\NI'll follow you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much mana left...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like the other heroes.\NYou actually came prepared to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki didn't have that,\Nand it held our party back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't like being all on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back, Kaori! You can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:21:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't matter, then I want\Nto be by your side, Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I couldn't keep\Nmy promise, Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two're still good friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:05.07,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning," "Good night,"\Nall those simple things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:10.16,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,are so dreamlike and beloved to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:14.87,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I finally met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:21.50,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is so special, thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:29.64,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be lonely all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:34.85,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until you found me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:40.44,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:45.86,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until I thought of a world without you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:52.70,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?\NI miss you, I'm so fond of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:58.50,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, don't forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:03.59,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine bright like the first star in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:09.38,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,and stay closer to me than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:14.76,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:20.27,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of that hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:27.82,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by my side and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Arifureta: From Commonplace\Nto World's Strongest